            "title": "Our Team",
            "subtitle": "Founder and Principal",
            "text": "<p>In 2007 our journey began in Zahra's garage with a single carpenter. From at-home exhibitions to our first rented workshop in Kemari, we have steadily grown into a celebrated brand with a global reach. Today our team is made up of over 50 individuals, proudly operating out of a custom-built workshop in Korangi Industrial Area.</p><p>We take pride in fostering a community where our employees feel confident and actively participate in decision-making. We credit our growth to our investment in people and delight in each other's personal accomplishments — the mithai tastes all the sweeter when a team member brings in good news!</p>"
          }
        },
        "highlight_xQ7dDL": {
