            "title": "Zahra Ebrahim",
            "subtitle": "Founder and Principal",
            "text": "<p>Our work can be experienced in some of the country's most prominent spaces — from Islamabad Airport to the Presidential House. Each project is a testament to our attention to detail and our passion for design excellence.</p>"
          }
        },
